  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC282">
        <l>naṉṟiṟ ṟēyu maṉṟīṟ ṟēyu</l>
        <l>mantīṟ ṟōvu maṉṉīṟ ṟōvu</l>
        <l>maṉṉa piṟavuṅ kuṟippoṭu koḷḷum.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/171/mode/1up">171</ref>.</p>
      <p>
ituvum collutaṟ kuṟippiṉāl poruḷ vēṟupaṭum iṭaiccoṟḷai uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
varalāṟu:
      </p>
      <p>
naṉṟīṟṟu ē:
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC282-Ilam-cit1">
        <l>‘naṉṟē naṉṟē’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉa varum.
      </p>
      <p>
aṉṟīṟṟu ē:
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC282-Ilam-cit2">
        <l>‘aṉṟē aṉṟē’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉa varum.
      </p>
      <p>
antīṟṟu ō:
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC282-Ilam-cit3">
        <l>‘antō antō’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉa varum.
      </p>
      <p>
aṉṉīṟṟu ō:
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC282-Ilam-cit4">
        <l>‘aṉṉō aṉṉō’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉa varum.  (34)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tāmōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n221/mode/1up">218</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n222/mode/1up">219</ref>.</p>
      <p>
naṉṟīṟṟēyum aṉṟīṟṟēyumāvaṉa naṉṟē aṉṟē eṉpaṉa. antīṟṟōvum aṉṉīṟṟōvumāvaṉa antō aṉṉō eṉpaṉa. naṉṟiṉatīṟṟiṉkaṇ ēyeṉa viriyum. ivvirivu ēṉaiyavaṟṟiṟkumokkum. naṉṟīṟṟēyeṉpataṉāṉ “nammūrntu varūu mikara vaikāramum” eṉpuḻippōlac coṉmuḻuvatuṅkoḷḷappaṭum. oḻintaṉavumaṉṉa.
      </p>
      <p>
kuṟippoṭukoḷḷumeṉṟatu, mēlatupōla ivaiyuṅ kuṟippōcaiyāṟ poruḷuṇarttumeṉṟavāṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
        oruvaṉ oṉṟuraittavaḻi ataṟku mēvātāṉ
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC282-Cena-cit1">
        <l>naṉṟē naṉṟē,</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC282-Cena-cit2">
        <l>aṉṟēyaṉṟē</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
        eṉa aṭukkalum varum; avai mēvāmaikkuṟippu viḷakkum.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC282-Cena-cit3">
        <l>avaṉaṉṟēyituceyvāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉa aṭukkātu niṉṟavaḻi, aṉṟīṟṟēvukkut teḷivu mutalākiya piṟaporuḷumpaṭum. ēṉaiyiraṇṭum aṭukkiyum aṭukkātum iraṅkaṟkuṟippu veḷippaṭukkum. ivaiyuntattaṅkuṟippiṟ poruḷ ceykuvaṉa.
      </p>
      <p>
aṉṉapiṟavumeṉṟataṉāṉ,
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC282-Cena-cit4">
        <l>atō atō,</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC282-Cena-cit5">
        <l>cōcō,</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="tolC282-Cena-cit6">
        <l>okkum okkum</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉṉuntoṭakkattaṉa koḷka.	(34)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Nacciṉārkkiṉiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Irāma. Kōvintacāmipiḷḷai</persName> 1997, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/307/mode/1up">307</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/309/mode/1up">309</ref>.</p>
      <p>
  colluvāṉ kuṟippōṭu poruḷ uṇarttuvaṉa
      </p>
      <lg>
        <l>naṉṟiṟ ṟēyu maṉṟīṟ ṟēyu</l>
        <l>mantīṟ ṟōvu maṉṉīṟ ṟōvum</l>
        <l>aṉṉa piṟavuṅ kuṟippoṭu koḷḷum.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
ituvumatu.
      </p>
      <p>
(i-ḷ.) naṉṟu īṟṟu ēyum ― naṉṟiṉa tīṟṟiṉkaṇ vanta vēyum, aṉṟīṟ ṟēyum ― aṉṟiṉa tīṟṟiṉ kaṇ vanta vēyum, antīṟ ṟōvum ― antiṉa tīṟṟiṉkaṇ vanta vōvum, aṉṉīṟṟōvum ― aṉṉiṉa tīṟṟiṉkaṇ vanta ōvum, aṉṉa piṟavuṅ kuṟippoṭu koḷḷum ― avai pōlvaṉa piṟavuñ colluvāṉ kuṟippoṭu poruḷuṇartti niṟkumeṉṟavāṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
oruvaṉ, ‘kolai, kaḷavu, kaḷ, kāmam, poy yeṉpaṉavaṟṟai virumpuka,’ eṉṟavaḻi, ‘avaṟṟai virumputa ṉaṉṟē! yeṉṟāl mēvāmaik kuṟippuṇarttum.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC282-Nacc-cit2">
       <l>‘niṉṟē yeṟipa paṟaiyiṉai ― naṉṟē kāṇ’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
(nālaṭi) eṉpatu, tīteṉṉuṅ kuṟippuṇarttum.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC282-Nacc-cit3">
        <l>‘iḵtūḻaṉṟē!’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
yeṉṟā laḵtiṅṅaṉam nukarviyātoḻiyumō, veṉṉuṅ kuṟippuṇarttum.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC282-Nacc-cit4">
        <l>‘antō! ventai yaṭaiyāp pōril’<note place="foot">(peyaril)</note></l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC282-Nacc-cit5">
        <l>‘aṉṉō! veṉṉā vatukol tāṉē!’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉapaṉa irakkak kuṟippuṇarttum.
      </p>
      <p>
ivvēkāra vōkāraṅkaḷ palacollō ṭaṭuttu varātu iccoṟkaḷaiyē yaṭuttup poruḷ vēṟupaṭṭu niṟṟali ṉavaṟṟaip (peyar) pēr tantu vēṟu kūṟiṉār.
      </p>
      <p>
‘aṉṉa piṟavu’meṉṟataṉāṉ’
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC282-Nacc-cit6">
        <l>‘aṉṉā! alamarum āruyirum’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpuḻi ‘aṉṉā’ irakkak kuṟippuṇarttutal koḷka.
      </p>
      <p>
itaṉai ōkāra mākāramāyt tirinta teṉṟalumām.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC282-Nacc-cit7">
       <l>‘ē e ivaḷorutti pēṭiyō veṉṟār’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉa vēkārattiṉ piṉvanta ē iḻi puṇarttutalum.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC282-Nacc-cit8">
       <l>‘a ā, viḻantāṉ!’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉavum
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC282-Nacc-cit9">
       <l>‘aiyāveṉṉai yāveṉ ṉaiyā vakaṉṟaṉaiyē!’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉavum
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC282-Nacc-cit10">
       <l>āvammā ammāveṉ ammā vakaṉṟaṉaiyē!</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉavum ākāra mirakkak kuṟippuṇarttutalum, piṟavum koḷka.  <num xml:lang="en">(34)</num>
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Teyvaccilaiyār</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">1929, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n188/mode/1up">181</ref>.</p>
      <p>
ēkāra ōkāraṅkaṭku eytiyatōr vēṟupāṭu uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
i-ḷ: ― naṉṟu, aṉṟu eṉpavaṟṟiṉkaṇ varum ēkāramum, antu, aṉ eṉpavaṟṟiṉkaṇ varum ōkāramum, attaṉmaiya piṟavum mēṟkūṟiyavāṟṟāṉaṉṟik kuṟippup poruḷōṭum ēṟkum. e-ṟu. ummai iṟantatu taḻīiyiṟṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
u-m:― 
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC282-Tey-cit1">
        <l>ceṉṟē yeṟipa vorukāl ciṟuvarai</l>
        <l>niṉṟē yaṟaipa paṟaiyiṉai ― naṉṟēkāṇ</l>
        <l>mukkālaik koṭṭiṉuḷ mūṭittīk koṇṭeḻu</l>
        <l>cettāraic cāvār cumantu.</l>
        <trailer>(nālaṭi-24)</trailer>
      </lg>
      <p>
itaṉuḷ naṉṟē kāṇ eṉpatu tītē kāṇ eṉṉuṅ kuṟippuṇarttiṟṟu. “niṉ............ṉṟē tirumukkuṭaiyar” eṉṟavaḻi a(ṉṟēye)ṉpatu allāmaiyaik kuṟiyātu mukkuṭaiyāṉaiyē cuṭṭi niṉṟu avaṉ kēṭpatu payaṉāka vantatu.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC282-Tey-cit2">
       <l>“poṉṉē koṭuttum”</l>
       <trailer>(nālaṭi―162)</trailer>
      </lg>
      <p>
        eṉpataṉuḷ, aṉṉō eṉpatu aruḷ kuṟittu niṉṟatu.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC282-Tey-cit3">
        <l>“ventiṟaṟ kūṟṟam perumpē tuṟuppa―</l>
        <l>antō vaḷiyeṉ vantaṉeṉ maṉṟa”<note place="foot">puṟam-238.</note></l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉṟavaḻi, antō eṉpatu kēṭu kuṟittu niṉṟatu. aṉṉa piṟavu māvaṉa vantavaḻik kaṇṭu koḷka.	[33]
      </p>
    </body>
